sh team they spanked 3-0 a few months is sitting pretty at Numero Uno.<\\/p>\",\"20\":\"\",\"14\":\"\",\"16\":\"\",\"10\":[\"7\"]}}', '2013-10-11 19:08:27', '2013-10-11 19:08:27', '7f23b4b8-65ad-466d-bebe-9859656d40da'),
